## 4ï¸âƒ£ File Permissions & Ownership

### ğŸ”¹ Commands

* `chmod`
* `chown`
* `chgrp`
* `umask`

### ğŸ”¹ DevOps Scenarios

* Fix *Permission Denied* issues
* Secure secrets and config files
* Resolve CI/CD execution failures

### ğŸ‘‰ Scenario

```bash
chmod 755 deploy.sh
chown ec2-user:ec2-user deploy.sh
```

### ğŸ“Œ Points to Remember

* Executable scripts need `+x`
* CI/CD failures are often permission-related
* Never give `777` in production
* Understand numeric vs symbolic permissions

