## 7ï¸âƒ£ Process Management

### ğŸ”¹ Commands

* `ps`, `top`, `htop`
* `kill`, `pkill`
* `nice`, `renice`
* `jobs`, `bg`, `fg`

### ğŸ”¹ DevOps Scenarios

* Kill stuck services
* Debug high CPU/memory usage
* Manage background jobs

### ğŸ‘‰ Scenario

```bash
