## 9ï¸âƒ£ Disk & Storage

### ğŸ”¹ Commands

* `df -h`
* `du -sh`
* `lsblk`
* `mount`, `umount`
* `free -m`

### ğŸ”¹ DevOps Scenarios

* Disk full alerts
* Log growth issues
* App crashes due to no space

### ğŸ‘‰ Scenario

```bash
