## ğŸ”¥ Most Common Production Issues (Quick Recall)

| Issue             | Commands           |
| ----------------- | ------------------ |
| Port conflict     | `ss -tuln`, `kill` |
| Permission denied | `chmod`, `chown`   |
| Disk full         | `df -h`, `du -sh`  |
| App crash         | `journalctl`       |
| CPU high          | `top`, `ps aux`    |
| Service down      | `systemctl status` |

